title: US Lawn Mower Racing Finals
description: Lawn mower racing is one of the last affordable action sports. Lawn mower racers know the value of good filtration, that is why K&N is nearly everywhere on the track. K&N caught up with these weekend warriors at the 17th Annual STA-BIL Nationals in Delaware, Ohio at the Delaware County Fairgrounds.
